$NetBSD: README.Haiku,v 1.4 2025/03/29 15:44:07 nia Exp $

As of 2025, Haiku R1/beta5 with GCC 13 has been tested and works.

Due to restrictions on the root file system, the default PREFIX of
/usr/pkg is unsuitable. Either bootstrap with --unprivileged,
or use a different PREFIX:

	./bootstrap --prefix /boot/pkg
